CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FCrew personnel aboard two vessels
OL,7,Fwhich collided and led to the deaths
OL,8,Fof three fishermen were "distracted"
OL,9,Fby other operational needs, a marine
OL,10,Fsafety investigation has revealed.
OL,12,FThe L'Ecume II Marine Safety
OL,13,FInvestigation Report summarises the
OL,14,Finvestigation into the collision
OL,15,Fbetween Commodore Goodwill and L'Ecume
OL,16,FII on 8 December 2022.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FThe collision led to the deaths of
OL,7,Fthree fishermen aboard L'Ecume II and
OL,8,Fresulted in Commodore's Second
OL,9,FOfficer, Lewis Peter Carr, being
OL,10,Fjailed for endangering ships,
OL,11,Fstructures, or individuals, contrary
OL,12,Fto Jersey's Shipping Law.
OL,14,FThe report, carried out by the Bahamas
OL,15,FMaritime Authority (BMA) and the
OL,16,FGovernment of Jersey, found that as
OL,17,FL'Ecume II was not engaged in fishing,
OL,18,Fboth vessels should have been sailing
OL,19,F"with the purpose of avoiding a
OL,20,Fcollision".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FThe report found that when the two
OL,7,Fvessels were less than one nautical
OL,8,Fmile apart, both altered course:
OL,9,FL'Ecume II adjusted to port (left), as
OL,10,FCommodore turned starboard (right).
OL,12,FTwo minutes later, the vessels
OL,13,Fcollided, with L'Ecume II sinking
OL,14,Fmoments later.
OL,16,FThe investigation found that neither
OL,17,Fvessel made the required sound signals
OL,18,Fto show they were altering course, and
OL,19,F"apparently lacked awareness of what
OL,20,Fthe other was doing".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FWhile Commodore sounded the signal for
OL,7,Fwhen a collision threat is present,
OL,8,Fthis only came eight seconds before
OL,9,Fimpact.
OL,11,FThe report also found that the officer
OL,12,Fof the watch, Lewis Carr, had a poor
OL,13,Fradio setup, which "was not optimised
OL,14,Ffor collision avoidance".
OL,16,F"His decision to monitor the situation
OL,17,F'by eye' deprived him of a more
OL,18,Faccurate appraisal that might have
OL,19,Fbeen possible using other means that
OL,20,Fwere available," the report reads.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FThe investigation also found that Carr
OL,7,Fwas showing signs of fatigue, which
OL,8,Fcontributed to the collision.
OL,10,FThe Second Officer was on a phone call
OL,11,Fas both vessels changed course, which
OL,12,Fled to a "general failure to
OL,13,Fappreciate the seriousness of the
OL,14,Fdeveloping close-quarters situation".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,F"His focus on completing the pre-
OL,7,Farrival checklist, misjudgement of the
OL,8,Feffectiveness of the alteration of
OL,9,Fcourse, and subsequent passing
OL,10,Fdistance (...) indicate that fatigue
OL,11,Fwas likely a significant contributing
OL,12,Ffactor in the collision," the report
OL,13,Fexplains.
OL,15,FIn terms of L'Ecume II, the report
OL,16,Ffound that the vessel's skipper,
OL,17,FMichael Michieli, was "almost
OL,18,Fcertainly" in the generator room
OL,19,Finvestigating an electrical fault.
OL,26,@rD@JpmrD@Npn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FHowever, this meant that no
OL,7,Fcertificated watchkeeper was on the
OL,8,Fbridge.
OL,10,FIt is unknown why L'Ecume II altered
OL,11,Fits course, but the movement was
OL,12,Fdescribed as contrary to collision
OL,13,Fregulations and was "neither
OL,14,Fanticipated nor readily apparent to
OL,15,FCommodore Goodwill".
OL,17,FThe report states that lessons are to
OL,18,Fbe learned, calling for lookouts to be
OL,19,Fpresent and available on all vessels.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780686673
OL,3,CFatigue played factor into fatal boat
OL,4,Ccollision which caused three deaths
OL,6,FIt also recommends that the States of
OL,7,FJersey amend its legislation to not
OL,8,Frestrict publishing these types of
OL,9,Finvestigations, which is sometimes the
OL,10,Fcase in serious maritime incidents.
OL,12,F"Fishing vessels and their crews carry
OL,13,Fa disproportionate risk when they are
OL,14,Finvolved in collisions," the report
OL,15,Fconcludes. "Further work needs to be
OL,16,Fdone in the international community to
OL,17,Freduce these risks."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
